USING 4X4 KEYPAD WIITH STM32 :

- ROW IN OUTPUT MODE  PC0-PC3
- COLUMN GPIO IN INPUT MODE PC4-PC7

- The pins in ROW (PC0 - PC3) should be connected with the PULL-UP register, to avoid the voltage fluctuation(0-5v).

- Enable the CLK for AHB1ENR in RCC.
- Configure the ports MODER, ODR, IDR, PUPDR
- Enable the peripheral CLK for GPIOC on RCC
- Configure GPIO PC0-PC3 and PC4 - PC7.

